Just stay here and guard Yin Palace.

94
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,680
Leave the rest to me.

95
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:11,010
- But...
- Enough. Stop worrying about this.

96
00:09:12,630 --> 00:09:15,110
We haven't seen each other in so long.

97
00:09:15,110 --> 00:09:18,290
Let's talk about something pleasant, all right?

98
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,710
All right.

99
00:09:20,710 --> 00:09:22,310
Come.

100
