104
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,535
Understood.

105
00:09:35,535 --> 00:09:38,110
Also, Madam Ye's younger sister, Ye Cang Lan,

106
00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:40,680
seems to be looking for dirt
on the Shi family to use against us.

107
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:42,710
She has always been willful and reckless.

108
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:45,540
She could endanger our plans.

109
00:09:45,540 --> 00:09:47,560
Don't touch her yet.

110
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:50,540
Ye Ru Ling is a useful blade.

111
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:54,420
I intend to keep a firm grip on it.

112
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:58,922
 

113
00:10:04,160 --> 00:10:05,790
You're awake.

114
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:13,790
Do you feel any better?

115
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,560
My head really hurts.

116
00:10:18,560 --> 00:10:19,920
Where?

117
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:22,580
My neck hurts, too.

118
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,590
And my shoulders...

119
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,930
Your shoulders?

120
00:10:33,750 --> 00:10:35,590
Just teasing you.

121
00:10:44,710 --> 00:10:46,890
Where are we?

122
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:49,900
Fenghua City.

123
00:10:50,560 --> 00:10:54,350
You are now Shi Yu Xiang,
mistress of this city.

124
00:10:54,350 --> 00:10:56,090
The Shi family?

125
00:10:56,960 --> 00:10:59,040
Have we infiltrated the enemy camp now?

126
00:10:59,040 --> 00:11:01,960
Fenghua City is in the outer territory
of Gengchen Celestial Palace.

127
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:05,040
Shi Yu Xiang may belong to the Shi clan,

128
00:11:05,040 --> 00:11:06,560
but she is not highly regarded.

129
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:11,020
She seems to be living quite a carefree and happy life, though.

130
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:14,160
She has always been arrogant and domineering.

131
00:11:14,160 --> 00:11:15,960
She built Fenghua City herself.

132
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:21,020
People outside even call it the City of Pleasure.

133
00:11:21,020 --> 00:11:25,520
You really gave me quite the role to play.

134
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:32,560
But since you've gone to such lengths,

135
00:11:32,560 --> 00:11:36,210
how could I let your efforts go to waste?

136
00:11:42,590 --> 00:11:44,780
Getting bold, are you?

137
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,870
Madam Shi, are you awake?

138
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:55,400
Ting... Madam Shi, the man outside
won't let me in!

139
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:57,200
What kind of racket is this?

140
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:59,860
If Madam Shi is interested in you, she will call you in to serve her.

141
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:01,230
I am her friend.

142
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:02,610
Hey!

143
00:12:05,350 --> 00:12:08,040
Madam, this man claims to be your friend,

144
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:10,590
but I have never seen him before.

145
00:12:12,870 --> 00:12:14,870
He is my friend.

146
00:12:15,470 --> 00:12:19,850
Madam, this man is rude, plain-looking,

147
00:12:19,850 --> 00:12:22,110
and even less attractive
than the one behind you.

148
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:24,690
Why would you be friends with him?

149
00:12:25,870 --> 00:12:29,680
I meant he was a friend of my friend.

150
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:34,070
In terms of looks, of course he cannot compare
to this one beside me.

151
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:40,180
Ting... Madam Shi.

152
00:12:40,180 --> 00:12:42,470
Hey, you on the bed.

153
00:12:42,470 --> 00:12:43,830
Madam Shi is up.

154
00:12:43,830 --> 00:12:46,350
Why are you still in bed instead of getting up

155
00:12:46,350 --> 00:12:49,750
to fetch water and help her wash and change?

156
00:12:49,750 --> 00:12:51,870
Tomorrow, I will send you
back to the countryside.

157
00:12:51,870 --> 00:12:54,380
How dare you?

158
00:12:55,830 --> 00:12:59,920
Since when is it your place
to tell my man what to do?

159
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:01,980
Please forgive me, Madam.

160
00:13:03,280 --> 00:13:05,160
Madam.

161
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:09,190
Do you want me to serve you?

162
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:13,380
No. Keep lying there.

163
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,710
And you, get out!

164
00:13:19,710 --> 00:13:21,460
Yes.

165
00:13:30,470 --> 00:13:35,400
Just now, Ting Yan's demeanor
felt strangely familiar.

166
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:39,520
I was just copying the Grandmaster,
projecting authority.

167
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:42,920
When have I ever acted like that?

168
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:45,690
Then I must not have captured your essence.

169
00:13:55,630 --> 00:13:57,360
Nian Jiu.

170
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:02,970
Ye Ru Ling is using you
more than she cares for you.

171
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:06,750
If you want a master to teach you how to live,

172
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:09,540
I can find another for you.

173
00:14:09,540 --> 00:14:11,800
From now on,

174
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:14,490
From now on, you are my only master, Grandmaster.

175
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:20,350
Nian Jiu, I've heard
Fenghua City is quite lively.

176
00:14:20,350 --> 00:14:22,230
Why don't we go out and explore together?

177
00:14:22,230 --> 00:14:23,580
Sure.

178
00:14:24,230 --> 00:14:26,490
I need to take you somewhere first.

179
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:31,630
Then I guess you'll have to go by yourself.

180
00:14:31,630 --> 00:14:33,290
I'll wait.

181
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:38,110
Did news of the new Spirit Fire come in?

182
00:14:38,110 --> 00:14:39,490
No.

183
00:14:40,680 --> 00:14:44,590
But someone is going to take me to it.

184
00:14:44,590 --> 00:14:46,440
Who?

185
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:48,010
Shi Qian Lv.

186
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:10,220
"Act as planned"?

187
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:19,060
Guards.

188
00:15:19,710 --> 00:15:20,710
Master Yuan.

189
00:15:20,710 --> 00:15:22,350
I will be away for a while.

190
00:15:22,350 --> 00:15:24,280
You must watch the Young Master closely.

191
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:25,490
Understood.

192
00:15:31,110 --> 00:15:34,490
Young Master?

193
00:15:38,870 --> 00:15:41,650
I will go kill that wicked Shi Qian Lv myself!

194
00:15:46,990 --> 00:15:48,990
- Madam Shi.
- Pick me, please.

195
00:15:48,990 --> 00:15:50,080
Madam Shi, pick me.

196
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:53,100
- Pick me, Madam.
- Please choose me, Madam.

197
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:55,920
- Look at me.
- Pick me, Madam.

198
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:57,150
- Look at me.
- Madam...

199
00:15:57,150 --> 00:15:58,210
Give me a chance, Madam.

200
00:15:58,210 --> 00:15:59,460
- Look here, Madam.
- Pick me.

201
00:15:59,460 --> 00:16:00,650
Please choose me, Madam.

202
00:16:00,650 --> 00:16:03,040
Pick me, Madam.

203
00:16:03,040 --> 00:16:06,590
- Choose me, Madam.
- Pick me, Madam.

204
00:16:06,590 --> 00:16:10,710
Grandmaster, why did you bring me
to Shi Yu Xiang's treasure vault?

205
00:16:10,710 --> 00:16:13,470
You never used magical artifacts before.

206
00:16:13,470 --> 00:16:15,580
Why are you suddenly interested?

207
00:16:16,800 --> 00:16:18,440
What is this for?

208
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:19,740
Defense.

209
00:16:26,440 --> 00:16:28,890
Don't tell me these are all for me.

210
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:41,630
I'll pass on this nose ring.

211
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:43,320
If I really put it on,

212
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:46,630
my beautiful nose would fall right off.

213
00:16:46,630 --> 00:16:48,220
This is a nose ring?

214
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:52,830
It's so big that it looks like
it's meant for cattle.

215
00:16:52,830 --> 00:16:54,180
I don't want it.

216
00:16:55,960 --> 00:16:57,440
I think it's fine.

217
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,820
I don't. No, thanks.

218
00:17:07,600 --> 00:17:10,250
Are these really all for me?

219
00:17:11,640 --> 00:17:12,980
Of course.

220
00:17:19,120 --> 00:17:21,550
But I don't like them.

221
00:17:21,550 --> 00:17:23,740
Forget it, all right?

222
00:17:29,070 --> 00:17:31,960
I can already hear you
cursing me in your heart.

223
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:34,200
My temper has been really bad lately.

224
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:36,380
I'm warning you, don't mess with me.

225
00:17:44,710 --> 00:17:46,710
What about this one?

226
00:17:46,710 --> 00:17:48,160
Do you like it?

227
00:17:48,160 --> 00:17:51,220
Yes, I do! This one's pretty.

228
00:17:54,030 --> 00:17:56,030
Too bad it isn't a defensive artifact.

229
00:17:56,030 --> 00:17:58,070
What's wrong with you?

230
00:17:58,070 --> 00:18:00,180
Do you really have feelings for me?

231
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:07,470
What's this?

232
00:18:07,470 --> 00:18:10,230
Pills. They don't taste bad.

233
00:18:10,230 --> 00:18:13,570
They calm the mind.

234
00:18:25,470 --> 00:18:27,180
Wow, I feel so happy.

235
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:30,310
 Greetings, Madam Shi. 

236
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:32,120
 Greetings, Madam Shi. 

237
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:34,070
- Madam.
- Madam.

238
00:18:34,070 --> 00:18:35,920
Back off! Leave me alone!

239
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:38,550
- Please choose me, Madam Shi.
- Pick me, Madam.

240
00:18:38,550 --> 00:18:40,900
- Madam...
- Don't you see I have one already?

241
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,940
I'm not putting on any of those.

242
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:10,030
Are you kidding me?

243
00:19:10,030 --> 00:19:11,710
Sima Jiao, you're hundreds of years old,

244
00:19:11,710 --> 00:19:13,810
yet you're as childish as a kid!

245
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:28,680
 Why is it suddenly thundering? 

246
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:31,620
 Even the weather is in a foul mood. 

247
00:19:42,020 --> 00:19:45,232
 

248
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:03,700
- Who goes there?
- How dare you damage our spiritual peak?

249
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:14,220
Father, another spiritual peak
has been destroyed.

250
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,360
Who did it?

251
00:20:17,360 --> 00:20:19,960
Someone at quite a high realm.
Our disciples couldn't catch him.

252
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,470
But the spells he used

253
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:23,750
carried traces of Sima Jiao's spiritual power.

254
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:25,850
So, Sima Jiao was behind it?

255
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:28,750
He's searching for our Spirit Fire?

256
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:31,620
Yes, and that's what worries me.

257
00:20:31,620 --> 00:20:34,070
By the way, Father,

258
00:20:34,070 --> 00:20:35,640
about the spy you told me to investigate,

259
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:37,230
after looking deeper,

260
00:20:37,230 --> 00:20:39,900
I discovered someone
who should have already been dead.

261
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:42,030
Who?

262
00:20:42,030 --> 00:20:43,420
Yuan Shang.

263
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:45,660
Yuan Shang?

264
00:20:46,470 --> 00:20:48,250
He's not dead?

